@localBaseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:9000/v1
@edgeBaseUrl = https://api-gb2260.xihan.website/api/v1
@baseUrl = {{edgeBaseUrl}}

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Area by code
GET {{baseUrl}}/areas/110101
Accept: application/json

### Children by parent code
GET {{baseUrl}}/areas/110000/children?year=2025
Accept: application/json

### Search active Beijing records
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=北京&status=active&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Search by level and year
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=东城&level=county&status=active&year=2025&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Areas valid in a year
GET {{baseUrl}}/year/2025?province=北京市&limit=20
Accept: application/json

### Changes by code
GET {{baseUrl}}/changes/110103
Accept: application/json

### History by code
GET {{baseUrl}}/history/110101?source=gb&limit=3
Accept: application/json

### Plate prefix
GET {{baseUrl}}/plates/京A
Accept: application/json

### Versions
GET {{baseUrl}}/versions
Accept: application/json

### Bad request example
GET {{baseUrl}}/areas/not-code
Accept: application/json
